{"tid":2223690,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"有冇人屋企曾經有過鬼？","createTime":"2020-09-30T04:30:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T15:03:16.000Z","uid":255802,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"26c8203367620d972ec549b4921a0f5da817b4f5","tid":2223690,"uid":255802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:30:30.000Z","msg":"我都幾肯定屋企以前有隻鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗰陣差唔多隔幾日夜晚都比鬼壓 有時好似聽到佢講嘢 但又唔知佢up 乜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有次甚至feel到有野吹我頭髮 輕輕摸我耳仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(嗰陣秋天 冇開冷氣風扇 都冇開窗)<br />\n<br />\n又有次瞓瞓下覺 比嘢捉住左腳踝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗住大聲尖叫 等屋企人留意到我 但喉嚨淨係發出到好細聲嘅氣音<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外屋企又會間唔時唔見野 多數揾哂成間屋之後 過幾日就會係<strong>當眼處</strong>出現翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋屋企有鬼嗰段日子 我又真係事事唔順意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過過左差唔多半年 隻鬼應該走左  生活一切又正常翻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20c2e8e44f1f9aa2244bb07806c5f7921dec5b18","tid":2223690,"uid":6783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:31:24.000Z","msg":"我"},{"pid":"e0746752c2724a774adf684dbb22ac57f8ccf297","tid":2223690,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:34:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5b19a8c2e66006bc40ad19a12c6257a8ad7121db","tid":2223690,"uid":7673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:35:52.000Z","msg":"瀨過"},{"pid":"bf84db94b0ef964ddce35060769a843f6f44839d","tid":2223690,"uid":8902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:36:29.000Z","msg":"同樓主一樣情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過係隻衰貓夜媽媽攪住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stretching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca900181f299d25c95228ba9af0eb533ae30934f","tid":2223690,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:38:20.000Z","msg":"鬼佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7abe38d969ce7d769ae15fc7dcb3db74d737603","tid":2223690,"uid":255802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20c2e8e44f1f9aa2244bb07806c5f7921dec5b18","tid":2223690,"uid":6783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:31:24.000Z","msg":"我"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:39:04.000Z","msg":"你老婆壓住你咋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52adf746f2952a2709aa57c016476fd1418a14b5","tid":2223690,"uid":153144,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:39:27.000Z","msg":"會唔會係你事事唔順意壓力大先鬼壓床呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71922fc6137b54f9b8a3560381c64cbe9734032d","tid":2223690,"uid":1646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:39:45.000Z","msg":"窮鬼計唔計?"},{"pid":"aa2b402577dede1e9ca5a8c62528199ef5ef97bf","tid":2223690,"uid":334722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:40:17.000Z","msg":"俾鬼砸係假既...同鬼冇關<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：近排撞完..."},{"pid":"8d9d9dd0528d18c0765b71ca88b55d7164caf4f1","tid":2223690,"uid":261388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:42:14.000Z","msg":"我以前同老豆老母住果陣經歷同你都係一樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最撚猛係隻腳比隻野抽起左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但係隻屋好旺我老豆，隻野裝修左之後就走左"},{"pid":"4cf5e66887419cab0c69618b2