sg":"More details <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81dc4b23597cbe92b0ef8e105cc97cb935d261a2","tid":2223690,"uid":378305,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:58:52.000Z","msg":"發夢有大波女鬼採陽補陰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9d2200c5b4d8469ea591eb6b10c9d8a9d71ce19","tid":2223690,"uid":132810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T05:09:49.000Z","msg":"有。幸好冇害我地。<br />\n<br />\n以前冇端端比生勾勾人害都遇過。撞到應一應。"},{"pid":"05d1c186f66bb52a3aff4754bc79987da6d0cdb7","tid":2223690,"uid":352555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T05:12:29.000Z","msg":"以前住長沙灣唐樓，d吊扇我地關左無啦啦開返<br />\n<br />\n我同家姐以前唔識世界，日日係度笑尻把自己開既吊扇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4dfc9027e0d8270a8e37729e5ebe6034692318d","tid":2223690,"uid":356078,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T05:14:11.000Z","msg":"同樓主經歷差不多<br />\n屋企人落過仔<br />\n我童年幸福快樂無壓力，但由小學開始晚晚俾鬼壓，直到上大學先停左<br />\n有一次貪玩對住張床講如果有鬼，今晚上來搵我<br />\n點知當晚瞓瞓下就有隻手好大力捉住我隻腳，我醒左想睇下隻手點樣，但我一起身佢就即刻縮左手，完全睇唔到係咩樣<br />\n之後仲係屋企聽到女人聲叫我，但唔係阿媽叫我<br />\n到中學買左相機係屋企試機，去到我間房一影就hang機，其他房無事，我死唔信邪係都要影，試左好幾次，影到張相入面有件衫遮左一半畫面，但件衫好清楚係粉紅色綿納，連佢格仔紋同車線位都影得好清楚，但件衫唔屬於我屋企，而且果時係夏天<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1183c5fa3ed5ceadd6a7d64a04b7c257eb95eb34","tid":2223690,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf84db94b0ef964ddce35060769a843f6f44839d","tid":2223690,"uid":8902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:36:29.000Z","msg":"同樓主一樣情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過係隻衰貓夜媽媽攪住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stretching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T05:18:44.000Z","msg":"隻貓責撚住你<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c949cae0e510ad10d69b80b88d332c7132f4066","tid":2223690,"uid":367566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"817c8423dc865f7a54ce8a4afe8cf24a0ccc025e","tid":2223690,"uid":255802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b6c1c0fcda412b75d41f70575fd783d69cd9031","tid":2223690,"uid":367566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:43:53.000Z","msg":"試過細個訓教<br />\n訓訓下發現有個細佬係我隔離<br />\n先前已經日日比鬼壓<br />\n有時唔係信呢d野<br />\n但屋企人曾經落過小朋友 <br />\n然後為左解因去左助養小朋友<br />\n最後平平安安<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:55:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我細個冇試過比鬼壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T05:23:41.000Z","msg":"師傅話過要幫屋企人積福<br />\n落仔聽講係唔太好"},{"pid":"11722ebec5a1df18a2747dbb235b17f753c267db","tid":2223690,"uid":24523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T05:37:04.000Z","msg":"屋企人去咗旅行（11月左右） 得我一個一屋企<br />\n我習慣瞓覺一定要蓋被 夏天熱到hihi都要攬住條被瞓<br />\n有晚瞓瞓下被風吹醒咗 <br />\n以為自己踢開咗條被 伸手去摸條被但係摸唔到<br />\n坐起身之後發現 條被摺得好整齊咁放係床尾 我對腳責住咗條被<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"386ba8cee04d27470b71ddede7d2bcfaf08456ff","tid":2223690,"uid":255802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05d1c186f66bb52a3aff4754bc79987da6d0cdb7","tid":2223690,"uid":352555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T05:12:29.000Z","msg":"以前住長沙灣唐樓，d吊扇我地關左無啦啦開返<br />\n<br />\n我同家姐以前唔識世界，日日係度笑尻把自己開既吊扇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T06:59:28.000Z","msg":"會唔會係屋企開咗窗有對流 所以啲風吹郁個風扇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faab0a1957120f710dacea28